# Los Angeles Crime Data Analysis

### Analysis of crime incidents in Los Angeles city area

The purpose of this notebook is to analyze the crime incidents that have occurred in the city of **Los Angeles**

The dataset has been obtained from the following source: [Los Angeles](https://data.lacity.org)

Los Angeles Crime Data Analysis

Analysis of crime incidents in Los Angeles city area

The purpose of this notebook is to analyze the crime incidents that have occurred in the city of Los Angeles

The dataset has been obtained from the following source: Los Angeles

paragraphs.text:
%sh

# create the local download directory if does not exist
mkdir -p ~/data-downloads
rm ~/data-downloads/*.csv

# create the required HDFS directory
hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/cloudera/data/raw/crime/los-angeles

# download the data from Los Angeles city data website
wget -O ~/data-downloads/crime_los_angeles.csv https://data.lacity.org/api/views/y8tr-7khq/rows.csv?accessType=DOWNLOAD

# copy the file to HDFS
hdfs dfs -put -f ~/data-downloads/crime_los_angeles.csv /user/cloudera/data/raw/crime/los-angeles/

# delete local data files
rm ~/data-downloads/*.csv

%sh

# download the piggybank jar from maven repository
cd ~/data-downloads/
wget http://central.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/pig/piggybank/0.17.0/piggybank-0.17.0.jar

# upload the piggybank jar to the HDFS jars directory
hdfs dfs -put -f ~/data-downloads/piggybank-0.17.0.jar /user/cloudera/jars/
